FCDAUD.translated: ~z~我们好像吃得太频繁了。下次吧。

FCDAUD.original: FCD_ACT_ANSWER_PHONE
~z~Okay, I'll come by and pick you up.
~z~I'm going to get some food. I wondered if you wanted to hang out?
FCDAUD.translated: ~z~我准备去吃顿饭。你想一起吃吗？

FCDAUD.original: FCD_ACT_CALL_DRINK_YES
~z~Drink? Again? You some east European alcoholic, son? Maybe later, man.
FCDAUD.translated: ~z~喝酒？又来？你小子就是东欧酒鬼？改天再说吧，兄弟。

FCDAUD.original: ~z~Sorry Dwayne - I can't do video games just now - some other time.
FCDAUD.translated: ~z~对不起 Dwayne－我现在暂时不能玩游戏－下次吧。
